+
+## Security Model Summary
+
+| Layer | Protection |
+|-------|------------|
+| **Container** | read_only fs, cap_drop ALL, no_new_privileges, non-root user |
+| **Network** | loopback-only gateway bind, bridge network isolation |
+| **Exec** | Deny-by-default allowlist, Telegram approval for all commands |
+| **Browser** | Deny-by-default allowlist, Telegram approval for all URLs |
+| **Secrets** | AES-256-GCM encrypted vault, never returned to model |
+| **Logging** | Full session JSONL, separate attack incident stream |
+| **Detection** | `report_injection` tool for model self-reporting |
+
+**What IS contained**: Container filesystem, exec without approval, browser without approval
+
+**What is NOT contained**: Mounted volumes (`~/.hyperclaw/*`), outbound network (use firewall/proxy for full containment)
